ORDER BY [a].[Priority] DESC, [a].[TryCount], [a].[NextTryTime]

    FROM [AppStudents] AS [a]
    WHERE [a].[Id] = @__id_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a0].[Id], [a0].[CourseId], [a0].[EnrollmentDate], [a0].[StudentId], [a1].[Id] AS [Id0], [a1].[CourseCode], [a1].[CourseName], [a1].[CreationTime]
    FROM [AppEnrollments] AS [a0]
    INNER JOIN [AppCourses] AS [a1] ON [a0].[CourseId] = [a1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[StudentId]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[RegistrationDate], [t].[Email], [t].[Name], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CompletionDate], [t0].[CourseStepId], [t0].[State], [t0].[StudentId], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CourseId], [t0].[Description], [t0].[StepName], [t0].[Id1], [t0].[CourseCode], [t0].[CourseName], [t0].[CreationTime]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [a].[Id], [a].[RegistrationDate], [a].[Email], [a].[Name]
    FROM [AppStudents] AS [a]
    WHERE [a].[Id] = @__id_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a0].[Id], [a0].[CompletionDate], [a0].[CourseStepId], [a0].[State], [a0].[StudentId], [a1].[Id] AS [Id0], [a1].[CourseId], [a1].[Description], [a1].[StepName], [a2].[Id] AS [Id1], [a2].[CourseCode], [a2].[CourseName], [a2].[CreationTime]

    INNER JOIN [AppCourseSteps] AS [a1] ON [a0].[CourseStepId] = [a1].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [AppCourses] AS [a2] ON [a1].[CourseId] = [a2].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[StudentId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0]

    SELECT TOP(1) [a].[Id], [a].[RegistrationDate], [a].[Email], [a].[Name]
    FROM [AppStudents] AS [a]
    WHERE [a].[Id] = @__id_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a0].[Id], [a0].[CompletionDate], [a0].[CourseStepId], [a0].[State], [a0].[StudentId], [a1].[Id] AS [Id0], [a1].[CourseId], [a1].[Description], [a1].[StepName], [a2].[Id] AS [Id1], [a2].[CourseCode], [a2].[CourseName], [a2].[CreationTime]
    FROM [AppStudentProgresses] AS [a0]
    INNER JOIN [AppCourseSteps] AS [a1] ON [a0].[CourseStepId] = [a1].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [AppCourses] AS [a2] ON [a1].[CourseId] = [a2].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[StudentId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0]
